data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER.
Welcome to the most beautiful house on the block. Built in 1907 and completely remodeled in 2015. This estate sits on 0.5 acres and is within walking distance of the square. Beautiful wrap around porch.
Bamboo flooring throughout the house. Master bathroom with claw foot tub. Spacious walk in closet. The driveway is made of original fort worth stock yard bricks. This house comes fully furnished and is move in ready.
WILL WORK WITH BUYER’S AGENTS with reasonable offers.

roof

floors
double pane windows
among many other things. house is full of character and is a showstopper.
